raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "nannos" %}
{% set version = "2.6.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://gitlab.com/{{ name }}/{{ name }}/-/archive/v{{ version }}/{{ name }}-v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 14468f86b63fdee9ad60b752dbd78d03aec98d7b525caba70fc4a7a86ce76be0


build:
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps"
  skip: true  # [py<39]

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.9
    - scipy >=1.0
    - autograd >=1.4
    - matplotlib-base
    - shapely
    - joblib
    - colorlog
    - psutil
    - ipython
    - nlopt
    - pytorch          # [not win]
    - pytorch-cpu      # [cuda_compiler_version == "None" and not win]
    - pytorch-gpu      # [cuda_compiler_version != "None" and not win]
    - magma            # [not osx and not win]
    - jax              # [not win]
    - jaxlib           # [cuda_compiler_version == "None" and not win]
    - jaxlib=*=*cuda*  # [cuda_compiler_version !== "None" and not win]
    - pyvista
    - ipywidgets
    - trame
    - trame-vuetify
    - trame-vtk
    - importlib_metadata   # [py<38]

test:
  imports:
    - {{ name }}
  source_files:
    - test/conda_test.py
  commands:
    - pytest -s -vv ./test/conda_test.py
  requires:
